    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reform use of non-disclosure agreements (NDAs) in employment",
        "additional_details": "The opposite view, that payments routinely reward false allegations, also leads to the same conclusion. These NDAs are inappropriate.",
        "background": "Settlements that include NDAs remain secret. This can perpetuate a culture of bullying and victimisation and allow abuse to remain unchallenged. All NDAs should explicitly say that employees or ex-employees are allowed to talk about any bullying and harassment they might have seen or experienced. ",
